'''彼得馬里茨堡機場'''（Pietermaritzburg Airport，{{airport codes|PZB|FAPM}}）是位於[[南非|南非]][[彼得馬里茨堡|彼得馬里茨堡]]的機場。

2013年航站楼和停机坪进行了升级改造。此外，一个距离彼得马里茨堡10公里的新机场正在规划中，该机场将可容纳宽体客机和货机。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sanews.gov.za/south-africa/pmb-airport-gets-makeover|title=PMB airport gets makeover – SA News|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307031408/http://www.sanews.gov.za/south-africa/pmb-airport-gets-makeover|archivedate=7 March 2014}}</ref>

2020年，在解除[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]的封锁措施后，彼得马里茨堡机场是南非政府授权为国内旅行开放的少数机场之一。<ref>{{Cite web|date=|title=More airports open for South African travel|url=https://businesstech.co.za/news/lifestyle/433899/more-airports-open-for-south-african-travel/|url-status=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025205425/https://businesstech.co.za/news/lifestyle/433899/more-airports-open-for-south-african-travel/|archive-date=2021-10-25|access-date=2020-12-03|website=Business Tech|language=en-US}}</ref>

